## Resource Plan (Free Tier Budget)

| Resource | What | Limit | Usage |
|---|---|---|---|
| **Groq** | Target model (Llama 4 Scout) | ~30 req/min free | Attack testing |
| **Gemini** | Target model (2.5 Flash/Pro) + Judge | Generous free tier | Attack + ASR evaluation |
| **AdvBench** | Dataset | Free download | 50-query subset |
| **LlamaGuard** | Guardrail testing | Via Groq free tier | Mitigation evaluation |

